data.description: Welcome to 142 Tennessee Ave, a delightful corner lot single-family home nestled in the vibrant community of Saint Cloud, FL, sitting at 1.2 miles from Lake Tohopekaliga’s Lake Front Park & Marina. This charming residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.  This well-maintained home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for families or those looking for a cozy retreat. The thoughtfully designed floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living spaces, making it perfect for both entertaining and daily living.  Enjoy the Florida sunshine in your private outdoor oasis. The spacious backyard features a privacy fence with 3 entry points, one of them providing access to the side road with a double door gate, perfect for trailers or large vehicles.  The backyard’s “L” shape, along with the front porch makes them ideal spots for family gatherings, BBQs, or simply unwinding after a busy day.  Recent upgrades include fresh paint inside and out, granite countertop on the kitchen cabinets and new roof installed on August, 2023.  This property is not part of a homeowner’s association (HOA), providing flexibility for homeownership.    Don't miss the opportunity to make 142 Tennessee Ave your new home. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, a growing family, or someone seeking a serene retreat, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Schedule a showing today and experience the allure of Saint Cloud living.
